      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lawas Robbeschus irr\nInhras Widdû/ tawi Uſtaiktaji\nirr tewi paſaul skaistu padarriſ-\nſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tce irr wiſſustawus Gal-\ndus ts Preedehn no Seenira\ndarriſſchi/ tee irr Zeedra-Rohkus\nno Libbanus nehmusch/ un Ma-\nſta Rohkus preckſch tewim dar-\nriſſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tamus Airus irr tee ie\nObsoleem no Balsana darriſ-\nſchi/ tawus Gehdektus irr tee no\ngluddeneem Elewantu Rauleem\ndarriſſchi / no tahm Gallahm\nRitium.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dahrgs Andeklis ar iṣrak-\nſitu Darbu no Egiptes bija\ntas Iſplattijums/ kas tew par\nSehgelt bija/ pasilla Sihde un\nPurpuris no tahm Gallahm E-\nlisa bija taws Apklahjums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tce Gedſhwotaji no Zih-\ndona un Arwadas bija tawi Jr-\nreji/ tawi Gudree ak Tirns eckſch\ntewis! bija tawi Latwineeki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tce Wezzajee no Geeba-\nlas / un winnas Gudree bija\neckſch tewis/ kas tarvas Laivas\nSchkirbas aistaiffja. Wiſſas\nJuhras Latwas/ un wiſſi Laivi-\nneeki bija eckſch tewis/ kas ar te-\nwim prezzejahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Perſexi un Lideri/ un Libi-\ncri bija starp tawu Kaxa-Speh-\nku/ tawi Kaxa-Wihri/ preckſch-\nturrains Brukkas un Dſelses-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Behrni no Ariv-\nnn taws Spehks bija ap\nus taweem Muhreem / u\nSargt bija us taweem Tur-\ntawas preckſchturrains\nnas uskahre tee apkahrt pe\nweein Muhreem/ tee darrija\npaſaul skaistu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tarsis prezzeja ar t\nar wiſadas daſchadas Pre\nSudrabu/ Dſelft/ Alu-\nSwinnu notikke tee tawē-\ngōs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jatwans/ Tubba-\nMeeseeks/ tee bija tawi\nnecki/ ar Zilwekeem/ un\nRihkeem irr tee ar tewim\nzejschees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No ta Namna T\nmas irr tee Sirgus/ un Ja-\nkus/ un Sirg-Ebsetus t\nTirgōs wedduſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee Behrni no De-\nbija tawi Prezzineeki /\nGallas prezzejahs zaar\nRohku/ tee atderve Glen-\nSobbus un Ebenzu Rohkus\npar Dahwanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sibrija prezzejahs\nwim ar tawa daſchada D-\nRuhbinus/ Purpuri un ra-\nDarbu/ dahrgu Andekli/\ndahrgas Sihles / un da-\nAkminaus notikke tee tawō-\ngōs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Juha un Israēta\nme tee bija tawi Prezzin-\nKiveefchus no Minnitcs/ un\n"
